Package jdkc_exchange

Class Membership

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdkc_exchange.Membership
  • public class Membership
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for authenticating Members of Groups. The Membership instance connects the Member to the Group and is heavily used to check that a Member is indeed in the Group. The Membership instance is unique per Member-Group connection, that is, one Member cannot have multiple memberships to the same Group.
